cleaned_text: UT](/physician/utah/west-jordan) Crystal Glaser Dr. Crystal Glaser is a Chiropractic Specialist in West Jordan, Utah. She graduated with honors from Western States College Of Chiropractic in 2015. Having more than 8 years of diverse experiences, especially in CHIROPRACTIC, Dr. Crystal Glaser affiliates with no hospital, cooperates with many other doctors and specialists in medical group Alta Vista Chiropractic LLC. Call Dr. Crystal Glaser on phone number [(435) 562-1513](tel:4355621513) for more information and advice or to book an appointment.
